{"tid":678373,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"郭秀雲爆吳綺莉想去加國搵卓林","createTime":"2018-05-26T04:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T06:25:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aacacfb8ec5057e9427ba96ab15694d736af832c","tid":678373,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:35:43.000Z","msg":"郭秀雲（Sharon）與唐文龍昨日出席啟動禮，宣傳周日舉行的沙灘清潔活動。Sharon的好友吳綺莉日前在社交網站表示收到電話被問「點解唔死」一事，她指對方近日忙於搬屋：「我哋有幾個朋友一齊同佢傾偈，知佢哋得閒幫佢搬嘢。」Sharon又表示沒有聯絡卓林，直言不擔心她：「我等緊佢長大同生性！覺得佢應該唔會有事。」又表示吳綺莉曾與她傾過想到加拿大找卓林，但覺得作用不大。<br />\n<br />\n身為愛心大使的唐文龍坦言關注海洋保育，指地球暖化問題愈來愈嚴重，擔心下一代如何過生活，笑言自己擔心環境多於感情事！他又指因病而未能參與清潔海灘活動，Sharon則表示待他康復後，會帶他往參與珊瑚礁普查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1YRn54yQ0Kj3eocXBirRYQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/c4f7bb7aca9bf014a4b937e54778c717\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1YRn54yQ0Kj3eocXBirRYQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fc4f7bb7aca9bf014a4b937e54778c717&h=b91526fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E9%83%AD%E7%A7%80%E9%9B%B2%E7%88%86%E5%90%B3%E7%B6%BA%E8%8E%89%E6%83%B3%E5%8E%BB%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E6%90%B5%E5%8D%93%E6%9E%97-214500773.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2583%25AD%25E7%25A7%2580%25E9%259B%25B2%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%2590%25B3%25E7%25B6%25BA%25E8%258E%2589%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2590%25B5%25E5%258D%2593%25E6%259E%2597-214500773.html&d=2aExcw5PoHOJBrg3cG3sSLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=92f12ae3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E9%83%AD%E7%A7%80%E9%9B%B2%E7%88%86%E5%90%B3%E7%B6%BA%E8%8E%89%E6%83%B3%E5%8E%BB%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E6%90%B5%E5%8D%93%E6%9E%97-214500773.html</a>"},{"pid":"5f11d988f51ed804b38b346df967ea3c71e6d9